  <brief_title>Observational Study of the Incidence of Pressure Ulcers on the Help Support of Prevention of Bedsores POLYAIR®</brief_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
      <agency>Centre Hospitalier Universitaire de Nīmes</agency>
      <agency_class>Other</agency_class>
    </lead_sponsor>
  </sponsors>
  <source>Centre Hospitalier Universitaire de Nīmes</source>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The support of help to the prevention of sores include a big diversity of devices. The
      clinical experiment of these support comes up against the problem of the large number of
      factors participants in the genesis of bedsores. Nevertheless, it seems to be interesting to
      estimate the incidence of bedsores in these supports, with control of other factors
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
